The paper discusses the challenges and responsibilities of using artificial intelligence and machine learning in a way that maintains the humanity of our models. This topic is most closely related to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the importance of considering human bias in data (cs.HC) and the societal effects of models (cs.CY, cs.SI).
